WEBVTT

00:03:28.784 --> 00:03:32.419
I would run to the bathroom
so I would not have to answer it.

00:03:32.907 --> 00:03:36.116
If it was for me, my parents
would say I'm not around.

00:03:36.140 --> 00:03:38.070
I spent a lot of time in the bathroom.

00:03:39.721 --> 00:03:42.192
And I hated introducing myself,

00:03:42.216 --> 00:03:43.825
especially in groups.

00:03:43.849 --> 00:03:47.225
I'd always stutter on my name,
and there was usually someone who'd go,

00:03:47.249 --> 00:03:48.776
"Have you forgotten your name?"

00:03:48.800 --> 00:03:50.377
And then everybody would laugh.

00:03:50.856 --> 00:03:53.006
That joke never got old.

00:03:54.727 --> 00:03:57.310
(Laughter)

